--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2D - Xp
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
root -l --web=off 'convert_2D_wiener_4ch.C(1,12,4)'     // RW==1, nbin_mom==12, nbin_cos==4
../bin/wiener_example wiener.root output.root 232 0.5   // C for 2nd derivative (2D cross section)
../bin/wiener_example wiener.root output.root 332 0.5   // C for 3rd derivative (2D cross section)
root -l --web=off 'plot_diff_xs.C(1,1000.,40.,1)'       // RW==1, XS_FACTOR==1000., NUCLEONS==40., zeropNp==1 (0p followed by Np)



Other options: 
../bin/wiener_example wiener.root output.root 2 0.5 0   // No-wiener filter (Ac matrix should be identity)

